Question: Dongguan Ang'yue Electronics Co.,Ltd. CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Dongguan Guangyu Electronics Co., Ltd

Product: Inductors

- Specializes in rod inductors, toroidal inductors, I-shaped inductors, common mode choke, filter inductors, SMD power inductors, and digital amplifier inductors
- Provides solutions for power supply, automotive electronics, telecommunications, medical devices, lighting energy, industrial equipment, and consumer electronics
- Production base holds ISO 9001:2015 and CE certification, ensuring high-quality standards and RoHS compliance
- Widely used in PFC power boards, switching power supplies, electric car chargers, solar inverters, and more
- Offers design, manufacturing, quality assurance, and engineering support
- Global service network and commitment to customer satisfaction
